column4: Is it though? I'll have two little demons to deal with, instead of just one.
You don't know how tiring it is just taking care of you.
….But, well, I don't regret it, not one bit. You may be a little demon, but taking care of you makes me feel so fulfilled.
And now that you're all grown up, becoming a man for my sake…
...I'll have our little baby to take care of instead.
